      fullInsight: "Venus in Scorpio loves with terrifying intensity. Casual relationships feel pointless. You want all of someone or nothing. Passion runs hot, jealousy runs hotter, and loyalty — once earned — runs deepest of all.\n\nThis is transformative love. Relationships that begin now change you permanently. Existing relationships deepen or break — there is no in-between. Financial matters take on emotional weight. Money becomes a measure of trust. Spend wisely, love fiercely, hide nothing.",
