      fullInsight: "Venus in Sagittarius loves expansively. Freedom in relationships isn't a threat — it's a requirement. You're attracted to people who broaden your world: different cultures, philosophies, backgrounds. Love becomes an education.\n\nSpontaneity trumps planning. The best date is the one you didn't plan. Travel romances, philosophical connections, and friendships that feel like adventures all thrive. The risk is commitment-phobia dressed as independence. Freedom and devotion can coexist — Sagittarius Venus must learn this.",
