      fullInsight: "Venus in Capricorn loves with maturity and intention. Flings hold no appeal. You want a relationship that's going somewhere — a partnership that builds something real. Status, stability, and shared goals attract more than charm.\n\nThis is practical romance. Dates that discuss the future. Love that respects time and investment. It sounds unromantic, but there's deep romance in someone choosing you deliberately, with full knowledge of what they're taking on. Capricorn Venus doesn't fall in love — it decides to love.",
